headline: DD Adds FilmTec MXP RO-8038-FF Element to its Dairy Portfolio
summary: DuPont launches FilmTec MXP RO-8038-FF for dairy processors, delivering up to 50% higher productivity and seamless changeover in mesh-wrapped systems.

headline: DuPont de Nemours Stock Outlook: Is Wall Street Bullish or Bearish?
summary: Due to DuPont de Nemours' strong performance relative to the broader market over the past year, Wall Street analysts maintain a bullish outlook about the stock’s prospects.
